Today, @wagnerlaneproductions produced the 2023 Mayoral Runoff Public Safety Forum. To see 1800+ community members come together to hear from our mayoral candidates, share their thoughts, and advocate for making our city safer was beautiful. No matter who you choose to vote for, make sure you vote for peace. ☮️

The only way to Welcome our new Mayor! Bringing the WOW factor to every event 🔥 No detail too small, no challenge too big.
 
To my right-hand @thekxperience and the entire @wagnerlaneproductions team.  I’m always blown away by our team’s ability to bring their all to every project, even though they’ve proven amazing time and time again.  Thank you for jumping in without pause, creating solutions, and consistently meeting our client’s goals. 
 
A huge thank you to our vendors @thisisuic @1440eventdesign @visioninbloom @thediamondeventgroup @bronzeballoons @epic.events.chicago @conniespizza @elischeesecake @soulandsmoke @justturkey.grill @mmeventplanner @tablescapeschgo @warsawdoghouse @garifunaflava1 @lalunachicago #Uncleremus @mejanivegancuisine @frontierchicago @chefjup @taylortacos @mariositalinlemonade @chicagofoodontherun @pronghorn.co @gcjmanagement @sodexogroup @castlepartyrental @bluepeaktents @ericabraceyphotography @belenaquinophoto @yoliechichi @iamnerdyshoot @picturemosaics @beckengravingdesignstudio @thedavisconnect @tff_productions @docmartyn @djdougchicago @bennythebull @fuzzygreendude @therealstaley @bhawktommyhawk @clarkthecub @shannonrovers @dachicagobucketboys @kraseroner @sentrock @darealicon @dwhite.originals @macblackout #deliverypointband @carpachosupercombo @drmccoy_thedj @jayilla @common and all of your teams behind the scene. 

We make an effort to work with the best of the best for all of our experiences, and it’s been such a pleasure to create magic with you. Thanks for showing up and showing out. 
 
To #ChicagoforthePeople @chicagosmayor @apsandassociates and @risestrategygroup, thanks for entrusting us with such a monumental moment in our city’s history. We imagine you had many choices, but we are beyond grateful to bring the vision to life!

We already know you know 👀 But allow us to RE-INTRODUCE our fearless leader @nicolemariechicago 
*** Cue the drum roll and red carpet***

Nicole Marie Pittmon, owner, CEO, and Principal Producer of Wagner Lane Productions, is your one stop shop for event production. She brings together the right people, incredible design, and carefully selected vendors, making attendees feel safe, honored, and celebrated. 

With over two decades in the field, Nicole is industry acclaimed “The Fairy Godmother” of Special Events, known for creating rich and flawless luxury experiences. She thrives on delighting her event partners and continually seeks innovative ways to surpass their expectations. She's your creative guide, turning event ideas into dazzling guest experiences.

#WeAreWagnerLane  #eventpros #eventproducer #worldwideartist #experience #creativedirector #eventdesign #ceo #bossbabesquad

Last night's @chiurbanleague 
Golden Fellowship Dinner left us utterly spellbound. Producing and orchestrating such a resplendent and culturally empowering affair in the heart of Chicago was an experience that resonated with profound honor and privilege. 

The evening was not just a celebration but a testament to our collective commitment to uplifting African American youth, fostering entrepreneurship, enriching education, and championing the advancement of the community. As we basked in the radiance of the event, we were moved by the impact it had on individuals and businesses.

To our esteemed partners, we extend our heartfelt gratitude for entrusting our dedicated team with the realization of your vision, and in doing so, allowing us to be part of this transformative journey. Thank you for the privilege of making a difference together.

#WagnerLane #downtown #chicagourbanleague #events #eventproducers #designers #industrypros #eventdesign #starstudded #fundraisingevent
